  "time_ut": 1660537193,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A derailed love affair",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A father of two children and a young woman have been in love. Both of them met with an accident while traveling on the tracks.",
        "The two who were hit by the train traveling from Badula to Colombo were injured and admitted to the hospital.",
        "The two injured in the incident which took place yesterday (14) afternoon have been admitted to Dikoya Hospital, while one has been shifted to Navalapitti Hospital and Yuvathy Nuvarelia Hospital for further treatment.",
        "The incident took place near Singamalai mine between Hutton-Kotakalai railway stations.",
        "Hatton police said the father of two is a 27-year-old man from Hatton- Ebotsili Estate and the 17-year-old girl is from Dikoya area.",
        "Both of them were walking on the railway track when they collided with the train coming behind them. Hutton was notified by the train controller and both were taken to the hospital.",
        "After this, during the investigation conducted by the police, it was revealed that the two were lovers. Ranjith Rajapaksa"
      ],
